NOTE ON DATA (not covered by the MIT license above)

The MIT license covers the CODE only. The connectome files under
`data/connectomes/` are derived from third-party neuroimaging data (Human
Connectome Project, Lausanne/Cammoun parcellation). They are subject to the
ORIGINAL data provider's terms, NOT this license. Before redistributing the
repository publicly (e.g. pushing to GitHub), verify the HCP Open Access Data
Use Terms permit redistribution of these derived connectomes and add the
required acknowledgement, or remove `data/connectomes/` and point users to the
original source. See `data/connectomes/README.md` and `docs/METHODOLOGY.md`.
